Package: CellAgeR
Title: Enhancer-Enriched Cell-Type-Specific Epigenetic Clocks
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Xiaolong", family = "Guo", email = "guoxiaolong2022@sinh.ac.cn",
        role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides enhancer-enriched, cell-type-specific epigenetic clock
    models for estimating DNA methylation age from beta value matrices.
    Includes utilities to generate DNA methylation age predictions, compute
    age acceleration residuals when chronological age is available, and access
    packaged example datasets and pre-trained clock coefficients for
    reproducible analyses.
